data.title: 2017 Edinburgh International Book Festival Brochure
data.meta_description: 2017 Edinburgh International Book Festival Brochure - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides information about sponsors, funders, and partners who support the Edinburgh International Book Festival. It lists lead sponsors, major sponsors, sponsors, media sponsors, and trusts who provide financial support. It also thanks publishing houses, friends and patrons of the festival, and individuals who have donated. Finally, it lists over 30 cultural organizations from around the world that are programme partners, supporting the international scope of authors and events at the book festival.
